message: What do you do when you feel the imposter syndrome ? And how to differentiate between if you are actually bad or or it's just a feeling ?

data.message: don't feel, don't differentiate, you are what you are w 5alas, a new one();

I agree with moataz .. Dont compare asln don't give urself a ranking
Always ask urself this question maybe it will relief u 3shan I know ur mindset somehow "will you stop getting better and being a better person if you are number1?" if yes then u gotta change this and work hard to change this .. If no then rankings dont matter as long as u are progressing
This was a good article on the subject: https://wordimpress.com/breaking-imposter-syndrome-isolation/
